DIY Crafts: 4 Easy DIY Candy Pens from candy wrappers! Here are some easy and fun ways to recycle candy wrappers and turn them into fun DIY pens or pencils.  In this DIY Craft video tutorial learn how to make 4 different cute pens by recycling candy wrappers.  Watch this DIY video tutorial to learn how to make 4 different cool & unique candy pen crafts.  I hope you have fun with this DIY candy pen craft idea.  You don't have to stop at these 4 kinds of candy.  Here are some ideas you could do - Jolly Ranchers, Gummy Bears/Worms, SKittles, M & M's, Licorice, candy cane and many more.  Enjoy this fun craft idea and get creative! Have fun with these cute novelty pens making project.  You could even do these with pencils! Go to school in style and prank your friends and teacher when you pull out crazy cute DIY pens that actual work!

What kind of DIY candy pen will you make? I would love to see your DIY creations.  These would make great DIY gifts/presents for friends and family.  Who wouldn't love to receive one of these decorative pens that are fun and don't involve glitter, pom poms & flowers? Make a personalized pen for any candy lover (make them their favorite candy pen)! Again, I would love to see your candy wrapper crafts!

