Supplies you will need for this candy wrapper DIY Craft:

Starburst Candy Pens:
Foam Block
Sharpie
XActo Knife
Pen
Hot Glue
Pack of Starburst

Snickers Candy Pen:
Snickers Bar
Brown Polymer Clay
Pen
E6000 Glue

Bubble Gum Pens:
Pack of Bubble Gum
Hot Glue
Pink Polymer Clay
Bubble Gum Flavoring
Pen

Rolo Candy Pen:
1/2 PVC Pipe
Sand Paper
Rolo's Candy


